---
title: Moroccan-Style Orange and Olive Chicken with Couscous Salad
description: Discover a world of flavour from the comfort of your kitchen. For this meal, we’re headed to Morocco with a sweet and savoury orange chicken and fluffy, tender couscous. Grab your ticket to flavourtown!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-aux-olives-et-a-lorange-a-la-marocaine-ecb64890.jpg
